node.text:
.
An award winning animation about the way countries fight their wars and visualized all the controversies, political motivations, different military assets and moral contrasts between these countries and the way they conduct war. We approached these subjects in a humoristic and satirical way to catch the viewer off guard.

node.title: How Countries Fight Their Wars By @mitsi.studio
